item.title: ICHC Ladies 1s battle UCL rivals
item.author: Jessica Purcell,
item.description: Ready for a re-match with long-time rivals UCL, we got to Harlington early, and had a good strategy session with Coach Oli, only slightly distracted by the un-named players who wouldn’t keep their shirts on. Ears ringing with assertions that we should play defensively and win with superior numbers …
